msgid ""
"PlasmaTube allows you to watch YouTube videos on your phone or desktop using "
"a elegant user interface integrated with the rest of Plasma."
msgstr ""
"PlasmaTube vam omogoča ogled videoposnetkov v YouTubu na telefonu ali "
"namizju z uporabo elegantnega uporabniškega vmesnika integriranega v Plasmo."
